hcc_text: Bartow Avenue is a pedestrian high crash corridor (top third for pedestrian deaths and serious injuries per mile in the Bronx)
info: At Bartow Avenue at Edson Avenue and New England Thrwy Sb Exit 11, there were 33 injuries in crashes between 2008 and 2012.
